Subject: FEATURE: add a new parameter to eliminate glitches
Date: Tue, 29 Jun 2010 17:20:10 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Add a new variable to the model generator which is the Minimum Time  
that a variable should be at a bin assignment to be considered stable  
at that bin value.

This can be achieved by checking each time the bin assignment changes  
for a variable that it states in that bin for the specified duration.

